{"tid":879440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少林寺弟子43秒KO非洲拳王？拳王身份被踢爆","createTime":"2018-10-28T03:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T04:41:01.000Z","uid":89543,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"38c999e070f45eb91bd058b32d765cf82082e33f","tid":879440,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:14:00.000Z","msg":"國5新設「宜4匝道」今下午3時通車 怎麼走看這裡...<br />\n快訊<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞\t<br />\n少林寺弟子43秒KO非洲拳王？拳王身份被踢爆&hellip;<br />\n2018-10-28 08:24<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n來自非洲坦桑尼亞「拳王」蓋博瑞（右），僅43秒就被釋延孜（左）KO。（香港《星島日報》）<br />\n來自非洲坦桑尼亞「拳王」蓋博瑞（右），僅43秒就被釋延孜（左）KO。（香港《星島日報》）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕為宣揚少林寺武功蓋天下，在中國「功夫之都」河南登封舉辦一場「武極天下&middot;登封造極」世界格鬥冠軍賽，其中一場少林弟子釋延孜迎戰非洲職業拳王蓋博瑞之戰，吸引約3萬名觀眾現場觀戰，<span style=\"color: red;\">釋延孜以43秒時間直接KO非洲拳王，當場中國觀眾歡聲雷動，但是，事後卻被網友踢爆，這名非洲拳王只是被雇用打拳的非洲留學生。</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，蓋博瑞已經承認自己根本不是什麼非洲拳王，宣傳所說的15戰中14勝1負也是假的，他承認，自己只是一名在中國的留學生，就讀於瀋陽航空航天大學，被雇用打拳，曾在中國打過6場拳賽，只贏過1場，但今年初已離校。<br />\n<br />\n被揪出作假，主辦單位也承認，在選手挑選審核存在紕漏，將來也擔補救措施。"},{"pid":"7d85362352303c5addbfd9f23c79cb21d3046e92","tid":879440,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/111443_ec4c502c6f64e77347d5006c6e92a2e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F111443_ec4c502c6f64e77347d5006c6e92a2e3.png&h=a81fe239&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d43e26c1cee4774c06941f42287c13183eda9ed9","tid":879440,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"三分鐘冇事 我放過你"},{"pid":"7f83d94ac1b36a6a4564fd1cd8d0a8cb54728ab7","tid":879440,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acc360bb87db3a7b21428f38af7fc45ba0a688a6","tid":879440,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"打拳都做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22634f1895d3dfebdf1c4ba57398139f164fd0ea","tid":879440,"uid":199417,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:17:06.000Z","msg":"姐係咁<br />\n人地就一身腹肌<br />\n你就一身肥肉<br />\n你話你43秒ko人<br />\n佢企定係度俾你打都唔知k唔ko到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8150c10d8ff8c57a12ad8212a75cf05c15bdb7a","tid":879440,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:17:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08c4349dd176b65cc99431d0b589e32dcfcccbe3","tid":879440,"uid":39855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"錢已袋，話之你。"},{"pid":"50c0d3598de465490915fccfe460398e6646309d","tid":879440,"uid":62646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:40:50.000Z","msg":"個少林友成身完美的脂肪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4354fd04d1b9797f4a22f6a44a76fe078ca078","tid":879440,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:41:01.000Z","msg":"真係同徐曉冬講既一樣，搵留學生打拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}